gree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係好撚貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f2e2f6390dd0d5ab7a63e0b9e3b88aafaf6963","tid":4810,"uid":47180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T16:35:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果大家對啲清新既香水有興趣，可以去sass/sogo試下呢幾隻：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Bvlgari</span> <br />\nAqua Amara 呢隻唔好太近聞，我第一次聞到覺得佢好將個海洋濃縮左係呢樽野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAqua Pour Homme Marine 同Versace Pour Homme似但偏向海洋既味會多啲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Versace</span> <br />\nPour Homme 有好多人話似Chanel allure homme sport 但我覺得呢隻fresh 啲冇咁濃冇咁甜都不失為好既選擇<br />\n<br />\nEau Fraiche 我覺得聞落似楊桃，幾甜既生果味，我覺得男女都岩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Salvatore Ferrangamo</span><br />\nFree Time 唔太持久但幾好聞，清新既檬味加啲薑既辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Giorgio Armani</span> <br />\nAcqua di Gio 用過都覺得唔錯，但我宜家手頭上冇，比唔到comment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上面幾隻都唔太貴，100ml大約400-600都有交易,50ml就400內，日日用既話一支都夠噴大半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n初頭覺得eau fraiche 係幾香<br />\n但我用多一排之後 覺得有d 普通<br />\n擺左係個櫃四年都未用晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nperry ellis 有支叫360 red<br />\n佢話同acqua du gio個味一樣咁滯<br />\n但係價錢平一大截 160蚊 100ml<br />\n有興趣可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15841e0a5990258f21e2ec3a0c2fde4c615fbba4","ti